- **Business Transfers:** Information may be disclosed and otherwise transferred to any potential acquirer, successor, or assignee as part of any proposed merger, acquisition, debt financing, sale of assets, or similar transactions.

**4. Your Choices**

You have the right to request access to or deletion of your personal information. If you wish to do so, please contact us at [evobio721@gmail.com].

**5. Third-Party Services**

The Application may contain links to third-party websites and services. Any information you provide to third-party services is covered by their privacy policies, not this one.

**6. Security**

We implement security measures designed to protect your information from unauthorized access. However, despite our safeguards and efforts, no security measures are perfect, and no method of data transmission can be guaranteed against any interception or other types of misuse.

**7. International Users**

The Application is hosted in the United States. If you choose to use the Application from the European Union or other regions of the world, then you acknowledge that you are transferring your personal information outside of those regions for storage and processing.

**8. Changes to This Privacy Policy**

We may update this privacy policy from time to time. We will notify you of any changes by posting the new privacy policy on this page.

**9. Contact Us**

If you have any questions or suggestions about our Privacy Policy, do not hesitate to contact us at [insert contact information].

